{"tid":2462650,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股壇老千明落廉政公署面","createTime":"2021-03-26T06:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T06:43:46.000Z","uid":357569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"223947af8fef68ae47e2cf31e2c21f628b05da8e","tid":2462650,"uid":357569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:35:42.000Z","msg":"曹貴子入稟告康宏環球誹謗兼索償 向法庭申禁制令<br />\n康宏環球1月初發佈了公告指前執行董事曹貴子透過循環融資及不當配股，為控制康宏以隱瞞其過失、操控股價及以康宏資金認購康宏股份，攤薄股東股權等，嚴重損害了康宏及其股東利益。曹貴子昨日入稟高等法院以相關言論屬誹謗為由，向康宏及其14名董事索償，並要求法庭發出禁制令，禁止其發表類近誹謗言論。<br />\n老廉都告唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家曹貴子告翻轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1532122/即時-港聞-曹貴子入稟告康宏環球誹謗兼索償-向法庭申禁制令\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F1532122%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%9B%B9%E8%B2%B4%E5%AD%90%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E5%91%8A%E5%BA%B7%E5%AE%8F%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E8%AA%B9%E8%AC%97%E5%85%BC%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F-%E5%90%91%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E7%94%B3%E7%A6%81%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%A4&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=93c481c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F1532122%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%9B%B9%E8%B2%B4%E5%AD%90%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E5%91%8A%E5%BA%B7%E5%AE%8F%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E8%AA%B9%E8%AC%97%E5%85%BC%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F-%E5%90%91%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E7%94%B3%E7%A6%81%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%A4&h=6ef4c4d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1532122/即時-港聞-曹貴子入稟告康宏環球誹謗兼索償-向法庭申禁制令</a>"},{"pid":"127050c1b1f1fbf5c8d20cbe7b880b318059ac19","tid":2462650,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"後